{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/5508_2","webpackCompilationHash":"b5f67fa8c2011b2b84ec","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5ca31378-f638-52e7-be43-0a6a9345f407","html":"<p>전자도핑 반도체와 홀도핑 반도체를 접합한 PN접합은 다이오드 소자로 이용된다. 대부분의 반도체 소자들은 PN접합을 한군데 이상 가지고 있다. 반도체 특성은 이들 PN접합에 밀접하게 관련되어 있다. 여기서는 순방향, 역방향 바이어스에 대해서 PN접합 다이오드의 작동 메커니즘을 알아본다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"이온-주입에-대한-dopant-diffusion-ion-implantation\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EC%98%A8-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9E%85%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-dopant-diffusion-ion-implantation\" aria-label=\"이온 주입에 대한 dopant diffusion ion implantation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이온 주입에 대한 Dopant diffusion, ion implantation</h2>\n<p>확산(Diffusion)과 이온주입(Ion Implantation)은 불순물 원자를 반도체 안에 주입할 때 쓰는 기법이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"ion-implantation\"><a href=\"#ion-implantation\" aria-label=\"ion implantation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ion Implantation</h3>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/0.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>Low-temperature technique으로 고 에너지 이온의 빛을 반도체에 비추면 격자\u000b원자와 이온들의 충돌이 일어나 결정구조의 \u000b왜곡을 초래한다. 그 후, 왜곡을 해결하기 위해 annealing단계를 거친다.(Ion implantation setup with mass separator)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>annealing : 고온으로 장시간 유지시킨 후 서서히 냉각하는 열처리</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"diffusion\"><a href=\"#diffusion\" aria-label=\"diffusion permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Diffusion</h3>\n<p>High-temperature technique으로 원자 수준에서 불순물의 이동을 고려한 것으로, 농도의 기울기(gradient) 때문에 발생한다. (Three main sources of dopants: gaseous, liquid, and solids)</p>\n<h4 id=\"gaseous-sources\"><a href=\"#gaseous-sources\" aria-label=\"gaseous sources permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gaseous sources</h4>\n<p>안정적이고 편의성 때문에 가장 널리 사용되는 기법이다.(<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><msub><mi>F</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>P</mi><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>s</mi></msub><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">BF_{3}, PH_{3}, A_{s}H_{3}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.13889em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.08125em;\">H</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.08125em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">A</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.151392em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">s</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.08125em;\">H</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.08125em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>)불순물 산화물(dopant oxide)의 결과로서 웨이퍼(wafer) 표면의 산소와 반응 후, 표면에 걸쳐 균일한 불순물 농도를 형성하고 실리콘 안으로 확산한다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"liquid-sources\"><a href=\"#liquid-sources\" aria-label=\"liquid sources permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Liquid sources</h4>\n<p>Bubblers와 Spin on dopant 두 형태로 이용할 수 있다. Bubblers는 액체를 산소와 반응시킨 후 웨이퍼 표면상에 불순물 산화물을 형성하여 수증기로 바꾼다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"solid-sources\"><a href=\"#solid-sources\" aria-label=\"solid sources permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Solid sources</h4>\n<p>ablet or granular form과 disc or wafer form이 있다. Boron nitride(BN) disc는 750~1100도로 산화되는 가장 일반적인 solid source이다.</p>\n<p><strong>Top</strong> : A single molecule moves around randomly\n<img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js7-01.gif\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p><strong>Middle</strong> : With more molecules, there is a statistical trend that the solute fills the container more and more uniformly.\n<img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js7-02.gif\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p><strong>Bottom</strong> : With an enormous number of solute molecules, all randomness is gone.\n<img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js7-03.gif\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The solute appears to move smoothly and deterministically from high-concentration areas to low-concentration areas.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"diffusion과-ion-implantation의-차이점\"><a href=\"#diffusion%EA%B3%BC-ion-implantation%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"diffusion과 ion implantation의 차이점 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Diffusion과 Ion Implantation의 차이점</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>장점</th>\n<th>단점</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Diffusion</td>\n<td>훼손(damage)이 없으며 배치공정(batch fabrication)이 가능하다.</td>\n<td>solid solubility가 한정적이며 고온공정이다.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ion Implantation</td>\n<td>저온공정이고 정교한 농도와 깊이 조절이 가능하며 공정 시간이 짧다.</td>\n<td>추가적인 비용이 드는 annealing process를 포함한다.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.differencebetween.com/difference-between-diffusion-and-vs-ion-implantation\">참고자료</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"이온-주입에-대한-dopant-확산-simulator-소개\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EC%98%A8-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9E%85%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-dopant-%ED%99%95%EC%82%B0-simulator-%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C\" aria-label=\"이온 주입에 대한 dopant 확산 simulator 소개 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이온 주입에 대한 Dopant 확산 simulator 소개</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.edison.re.kr/scienceappstore/-/scienceapp/Diffuse/1-0-0/view\">Dopant diffusion simulator</a>는 실리콘 기판 내부의 As이온이 확산되는 현상을, 파라미터로 받은 dose, energy, temp, duration 값으로 계산해주는 시뮬레이터이다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/3.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fig. 1. Arsenic Implantation, Dose split, Energy=80keV </p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>scatter : Magnetic sector SIMS</li>\n<li>Fig. 1은 As이온의 농도를 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>15</mn></msup><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1e^{15}cm^{-2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">m</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>,<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>14</mn></msup><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1e^{14}cm^{-2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">m</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>,<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>13</mn></msup><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1e^{13}cm^{-2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span c