\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>,<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>14</mn></msup><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1e^{14}cm^{-2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">m</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>,<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>14</mn></msup><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1e^{14}cm^{-2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">m</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 으로 split하고, 에너지는 80keV, Rapid thermal annealing이 1100도에서 duration이 60second일 때 SIMS analysis한 그래프이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/5.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fig. 3. Arsenic Implantation, Dose split, Energy=80keV</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Dual-Pearson Analytic Model</li>\n<li>Fig. 3은 Fig. 1의 SIMS 측정그래프를 Diffusion simulator를 사용하여 같은 조건에서 시뮬레이션한 그래프이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/6.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fig. 4. Arsenic, Dose split, Energy=80keV, RTA=1100C, Duration=60sec </p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>line : Dual-Pearson Analytic Model, 3-stream diffusion model</li>\n<li>Fig. 4은 Fig. 2의 SIMS 측정그래프를 Diffusion simulator를 사용하여 같은 조건에서 시뮬레이션한 그래프이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"result\"><a href=\"#result\" aria-label=\"result permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Result</h3>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js9.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js10.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>EDISON <a href=\"https://www.edison.re.kr/scienceappstore/-/scienceapp/Diffuse/1-0-0/view\">Dopant diffusion simulator</a>는 시뮬레이션한 결과로 이온 주입 상태에서 열을 가하기 전과 후의 그래프를, Arsenic<em>implant plot과 Arsenic plot을 통해 볼 수 있다. SIMS 측정의 RTA(Rapid thermal annealing) 전, 후의 그래프와 Diffusion simulator의 결과에서 Arsenic</em>implant, Arsenic의 그래프를 각각 비교해보면 1 decade를 넘지 않는 선에서, 크게 오차가 생기지 않는다. 따라서 학생들은 이 시뮬레이터를 사용하여 다양한 파라미터를 바꿔보면서 시뮬레이션해볼 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"실습-예제\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"실습 예제 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>실습 예제</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.edison.re.kr/scienceappstore/-/scienceapp/Diffuse/1-0-0/view\">Dopant diffusion simulator</a>에서 주어진 파라미터를 입력하여 Dual-Pearson analytic model그래프와 3-stream diffusion model그래프를 출력하시오.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js5.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Dose split\n<img src=\"/media/POST/5508/js6.png\" alt=\"image\">\nEnergy split </p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/5508_2","tagSlugs":["/tag/dopant-diffusion/","/tag/ion-implantation/","/tag/dopant-diffusion-simulator/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-09T22:40:32.169Z","description":"전자도핑 반도체와 홀도핑 반도체를 접합한 PN접합은 다이오드 소자로 이용된다. 대부분의 반도체 소자들은 PN접합을 한군데 이상 가지고 있다. 반도체 특성은 이들 PN접합에 밀접하게 관련되어 있다. 여기서는 순방향, 역방향 바이어스에 대해서 PN접합 다이오드의 작동 메커니즘을 알아본다.","tags":["Dopant diffusion","ion implantation","Dopant diffusion simulator"],"title":"PN접합 다이오드의 특성"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/5508_2"}}}